author: glenn
msg: Updated and tested the hook priority for mod_jk.
mod_alias will now parse the URL before mod_jk.
Tested to make sure mod_dir handles the request after mod_jk
so that use of a DirectoryIndex index.jsp works.
Set the jk_logger to use during apr cleanup to NULL to
prevent segmentation faults from bad file descriptors
mod_jk is now running without any problems on unix.
These changes will need to be tested on Windows.
